research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Because `gated` beat the matched `topk` control at `K=96`, the next single question is whether that advantage extends one more step down the support ladder; testing `ARCHITECTURE=gated, K=64, EF=12, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=1.6e-3` will show whether `gated` is broadly stronger across high-K frontier points or only wins near the very top end.","summary":"Round 36 changed the picture: `gated@96` is not just viable, it improved the frontier over the existing `topk@96` control, so the family has earned one more K-mapping round. Keep the anchored recipe fixed and step only `K` from `96` to `64`. This directly answers whether the `gated` advantage generalizes to the next adjacent frontier point. Read the full curve, not just the endpoint: if training remains smooth and finishes below the `topk@64` control (`0.1992608`), `gated` is a real high-K mainline candidate; if it drops back behind `topk`, then the family likely helps only in the upper-K regime.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the current family, keeps EF fixed at 12, and changes exactly one main variable: `K`. It follows the prescribed ordering because recipe tuning was already exhausted before K moves began, and `K=64` is the highest-value next probe after the successful `K=96` result.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 36 established that gated generalizes beyond K=128 by beating the matched topk control at K=96.","Round 37 should probe the next adjacent K point, gated@64 with the same signum/LR anchor, to test whether the advantage persists deeper into the frontier."],"next_hypotheses":["If `gated@64` also beats `topk@64`, continue one more downward K probe because gated is shaping up as the stronger mainline family across multiple frontier points.","If `gated@64` falls back behind `topk@64`, treat gated as a high-K specialist and preserve it mainly for K>=96."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/results.tsv:2:r1_1774523552	1774523552	ok	keep	0.16425763070583344	128	topk	12				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0001/round0001_standard_1774523312_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef12_k128_20260326_190838	4ccce2a53a68f3b5743408dec07209ecc2fad9e2			执行主线 topk 参考配方的 clean baseline，不开新 family，不改代码，不先动 K。用完整 env_overrides 显式锁定 ARCHITECTURE=topk、K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=12、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=8e-4 及其余关键运行参数，优先消除变量隔离失效风险，并建立 round 1 的可比较基线。	这轮不是为了直接拿更低 FVU，而是为了建立干净基线。风险是收益偏信息获取而非性能提升，但这符合当前“frontier 为空先补 clean baseline”的主线策略，也避免在没有曲线参考时过早调 lr 或换优化器。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0001_standard_1774523312.log
research/history/results.tsv:3:r2_1774523810	1774523810	ok	discard	0.17248131334781647	128	topk	12				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0002/round0002_standard_1774523570_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef12_k128_20260326_191257	c3d2f65e70de4e209899271789bfa997ea727b3f			继续主线 topk，不开新 family，不换优化器，不动 K。本轮唯一主变量是学习率：从 8e-4 下调到 6e-4，回答“当前 signum+topk 基线是否因 LR 略大而限制了收敛质量”这个单一问题。	这是按主线顺序进行的单变量 LR 回调，归因清晰。风险是收益可能有限，但相比直接换优化器或改 K，这一轮更符合当前策略，也更容易结合训练曲线判断是过冲/震荡还是单纯欠训练。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0002_standard_1774523570.log
