research/history/logs/agent_action_0062.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With the `gated` mainline stalled for nine rounds, the highest-value Round 62 matched architecture probe is `group_topk`: it preserves the same static decoder-library weighted-sum export contract and fixed `K=128`, while changing only support formation to a group-local winner scheme that could reduce selection complexity if reconstruction stays competitive. This probe answers one question only: is `group_topk` intrinsically strong enough under the matched `signum`/`2.0e-3`/`EF=12` recipe to merit any later follow-up.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `group_topk` and keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This respects the Round 62 policy: one probe only, one main variable only, and the full mainline recipe stays matched except for architecture. `group_topk` is a better probe than heavier multi-branch variants because it is directly LUTurbo-compatible and has a plausible path to lower online selection cost rather than only improving training-side expressiveness.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 62 uses the single allowed matched architecture probe on `group_topk` rather than expanding the search broadly.","`group_topk` remains directly compatible with LUTurbo because reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over a static decoder library; only the encoder-side selection rule changes.","The main deployment-relevant reason to test `group_topk` is not just FVU but whether grouped winner selection looks promising enough to justify later work on lower selection overhead under the same decoder contract."],"next_hypotheses":["If `group_topk` is clearly worse than matched `gated` at `K=128`, discard the family and return to the `gated` mainline next round.","If `group_topk` is roughly competitive, record it as a potentially deployment-friendlier selector but still return to the `gated` mainline next round per policy.","If `group_topk` unexpectedly beats matched `gated`, schedule at most one later follow-up after the mandated return to the `gated` mainline."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0090.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After the simpler low-rank single-stage selectors (`lowrank_residual`, `lowrank_gated_residual`, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`, and `lowrank_grouped_residual`) all failed against the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative remaining matched architecture probe is `whitened_lowrank_residual`. It keeps the same low-rank trunk and single-stage static-library residual decode, but changes only the residual conditioning before support selection. This answers a clean question: was the mainline gain coming from the second residual stage itself, or can a better-conditioned single-stage selector recover enough quality to be worth any further attention. If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then the current evidence favors the two-stage residual mechanism rather than more single-stage low-rank variants.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `whitened_lowrank_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"whitened_lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This changes exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, and keeps the mainline `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe fixed. `whitened_lowrank_residual` is a coherent remaining probe because it preserves the low-rank single-stage export path while testing whether residual conditioning, rather than an extra residual pass, is the missing ingredient. The risk is that the added normalization path may still not close the gap and may be less attractive for LUTurbo runtime than the current mainline, so this should be judged strictly as a worth-continuing screen rather than a new direction to tune immediately.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"whitened_lowrank_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 90 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `whitened_lowrank_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness probe for conditioned single-stage low-rank residual selection; the core question is whether better residual conditioning can substitute for the second residual stage.","Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not treat this as license to open a new whitening branch sequence."],"next_hypotheses":["If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a single-stage comparison point but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0207.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"quality_anchor_near_low_cost_boundary","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 来自单个静态向量库；在线只做单样本 top-k 选择，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时就是单库查表 + 加权求和，因此属于直接兼容。上一轮 factorized_topk 的 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 降本尝试被 policy 拦截，且当前 <0.5x 区域 FVU 明显受 scorer 容量限制；因此本轮固定 K=64、EF=2、optimizer、LR，仅把 architecture 从 factorized_topk 切到 topk，验证去掉低秩 scorer bottleneck 后，是否能在接近低开销边界的总成本下显著改善 FVU。预计 total_cost 约 0.56x，虽略高于 0.5x，但可作为最邻近的质量锚点，帮助判断 <0.5x 区域的主要瓶颈是否来自 factorization。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@K64 相比 factorized_topk@K64 明显改善 FVU，则说明当前低开销区主要受低秩 scorer 限制，下一步应考虑在更接近 0.5x 的边界上探索更轻但非 factorized 的选择机制。","如果 topk@K64 提升有限，则说明问题主要来自预算本身而非 factorized scorer，下一步应转向新的低成本 family 或更激进的小库/小K 结构，而不是继续在 scorer 形态上纠缠。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 是最干净的直接兼容单库基线，可用于判断 factorized_topk 在低成本区的 FVU 损失到底有多少来自 scorer factorization。","本轮只改 architecture，保持 K=64 这个当前最佳 <0.5x 邻近点的查表预算不变，便于归因。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"该提案严格满足单变量原则，并针对 r206 的 policy_reject 与当前开放假设做了最小转向。代价是总成本会从 0.44x 上升到约 0.56x，不能直接补 <0.5x 前沿，但它能高信息量地判断 factorized scorer 是否是低开销区 FVU 过差的主因。","summary":"切换到直接兼容的 topk family，固定 K=64、EF=2、signum、LR=3e-3，只改变 architecture，获得一个贴近低开销边界的质量锚点，用来判断去掉 factorized scorer 后 FVU 能提升多少。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0153.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r150-r152 的 matched architecture probes 已经依次表明去掉 second stage、去掉 soft-codebook、退回 topk 都会明显恶化 FVU，因此当前问题不再是 family 本身值不值得继续，而是回到主线后重新建立一个干净的运行时与曲线锚点：在保持主线参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，确认其 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续单变量 recipe 决策提供可信基线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 复现 0.0581 左右的终点且吞吐恢复到正常区间，则下一轮再进入单变量学习率或优化器判断。","若 clean baseline 仍出现明显慢速但终点稳定，则把近期问题归因为运行时吞吐波动而非架构退化，后续 recipe 评估必须继续把总耗时与 tokens_per_sec 作为硬约束。","若 clean baseline 自身终点或曲线形状发生漂移，则先停止扩展 recipe 搜索，优先确认主线锚点后再做下一步单变量扰动。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 已满足选择成本预算，K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与主线复验混杂。","r150-r152 的架构探针已经说明主线 family 相对近邻与简单 baseline 都有真实结构收益，本轮按规则回到主线。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分是训练更长还是吞吐更慢导致耗时上升。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"本轮不新开 family，回到主线参考配方做 clean baseline 复验，符合当前主线推进顺序。虽然这一步不直接追求更低 FVU，但在近期多轮 probe 与明显运行时波动后，先恢复可信锚点比继续做难归因的 recipe 扰动更稳妥。","summary":"回到主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，固定 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或 recipe 变化，先做一轮干净 baseline 复验，确认当前主线的真实训练曲线与运行代价。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0215.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"192"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214 已证明在 EF=1 下把 K 从 64 提到 128 能把 <0.5x 区域的 FVU 从 0.2583 压到 0.1968，说明当前低开销区的主瓶颈更像是查表预算不足，而不是 topk family 已经到头；因此本轮继续沿同一最短链路 family 提升 K 到 192，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.43x、明显低于 0.5x 的条件下，进一步压低低开销区最佳 FVU，验证 topk@EF1 是否还能继续向可用前沿逼近。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K192 在 <0.5x 内继续明显改善 FVU 且吞吐下降可接受，则同 family 的低开销前沿可继续沿 K 轴补一个更细点。","如果 K192 的收益很小但训练时间或 tokens_per_sec 明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 的边际收益开始耗尽，后续应转向新的低成本 family 而不是再加查表预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 是当前唯一已在 <0.5x 区域稳定形成两个可行点的直接兼容 family，且导出路径最简单，适合作为低开销主线基准。","r214 已经给出明确正信号：在 EF=1 保持 encoder 成本不变时，增加 K 能显著改善 FVU，因此当前最有信息量的单变量仍是 K 轴。","评估时必须同步检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认新增查表预算是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮延续已验证有效的低开销 topk 主线，不再重复被 policy 卡住的 lowrank_factorized_residual param_only 路线。选择 K=192 而不是先补 K=96，是因为当前任务优先级是尽快把 <0.5x 区域的最佳 FVU 压低，而不是细化已明显被 K=128 支配的中间点；风险是更高 K 可能带来吞吐下降和更长总耗时。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 192，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1968 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/round0076_standard_1774557081.config.json:2:  "architecture": "jumprelu",
research/history/logs/round0076_standard_1774557081.config.json:14:  "family_name": "jumprelu",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0211.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"reduce_total_cost_into_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 u_r 是 trunk 静态向量库，b_i 是 residual 静态向量库；部署到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时可拆成 trunk 库查表加权和与 residual 库查表加权和，两部分都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此属于扩展兼容。r210 在 K=64、EF=1 下给出 0.69x / 0.1256，说明该 family 的质量明显优于 topk，但当前瓶颈是 trunk 带来的额外成本而非训练失稳。本轮保持 architecture、K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 16，目标是同时压低 encoder 与 deployment 两侧的 trunk 成本，把 total_cost 尽量拉回 <0.5x 区域，同时保留一部分 low-rank coarse 表达能力。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 能把 lowrank_factorized_residual 拉进 <0.5x 且 FVU 仍明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则继续固定该 family，单变量扫描 K 或更小的 TRUNK_RANK 以补齐低开销前沿。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 仍无法进入 <0.5x 或 FVU 明显崩塌，则说明该 family 在低开销区的 trunk 分支仍然过重，下一步应回到更短链路 family，而不是继续沿 lowrank 分支推进。"],"notes_to_memory":["r210 证明 lowrank_factorized_residual 在低 EF 下具备高质量潜力，但 0.69x 的主要问题是成本而非效果。","TRUNK_RANK 是该 family 最直接的降本旋钮，且同时作用于 encoder 和 deployment，比继续调 K 更符合本轮把点拉回 <0.5x 的目标。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"该提案严格只改一个主变量，并直接针对 r210 暴露的主要矛盾：质量足够好但成本偏高。风险是 rank=16 可能过于激进导致 FVU 回退，但这是判断 lowrank family 能否进入低开销区所必需的高信息量实验。","summary":"在扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual 上固定 K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，仅将 TRUNK_RANK 设为 16，测试能否通过压缩 trunk 成本，把 0.69x/0.1256 这条高质量边界点推进到 <0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0003.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 2 的 6e-4 明显劣于 8e-4，说明当前 topk/signum 主线更像是欠步长而不是过冲；本轮只把学习率上调到 1e-3，检验更积极的步长是否能在相同 family/optimizer/K 下带来更快且仍稳定的收敛，并刷新 K=128 的 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕 topk 主线推进，不开新 family，不换优化器，不动 K。本轮唯一主变量仍是 LR：从参考配方 8e-4 上调到 1e-3，回答“signum+topk 在当前设置下是否更需要稍大的学习率”这个单一问题。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮保持单变量且遵循主线顺序，先把 LR 维度补全到高于 baseline 的一侧，再决定是否切 optimizer。风险是 1e-3 可能带来震荡，但这正是本轮要验证的核心问题；若曲线恶化，后续就有充分理由结束 signum 的 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 对比。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 3 继续只调 LR，补完 signum 在 baseline 以上一侧的步长测试。","r2 的 6e-4 比 baseline 更差，初步说明问题不像是 LR 过大，更可能是步长偏小导致收敛不足。","本轮重点看曲线是否出现更快下降且仍稳定；若 1e-3 出现明显震荡或最终更差，就可结束 signum 的主线 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 比较。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 1e-3 优于 8e-4，下一轮继续只调 LR，在 8e-4 到 1e-3 之间或略高处做细化。","如果 1e-3 与 8e-4 接近但更不稳，下一轮可结束 signum 的 LR 扫描，按顺序只改 optimizer。","如果 1e-3 明显更差且有震荡，说明 signum 的合适 LR 区间已基本摸清，下一轮应切到 optimizer 维度。"],"primary_variable":"lr"}
