research/history/logs/agent_action_0169.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; JumpReLU only changes the single-sample support/coef shaping before top-k, not the exported decoder basis. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one static trunk lookup plus one sparse weighted sum over a fixed residual vector library, with the learned thresholds used only in online selection. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost should stay within the `≤ 1.5×h×n` hard budget and remain below the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline. The single question is whether this thresholded low-rank single-stage selector is intrinsically worth keeping in the current low-EF deployable regime, or whether the mainline’s soft-codebook plus two-stage refinement remains clearly necessary.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is clearly worse than the mainline in both FVU and runtime metrics, discard it and return to `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round.","If it is somewhat worse in FVU but materially better in throughput or total runtime, record it as a lower-complexity compatible side branch, but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy.","If it is unexpectedly close to the mainline at lower selection cost, allow at most one later family-specific follow-up after the required return to the mainline."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility: `扩展兼容`. Export path is `U(Vx)` trunk lookup plus one sparse residual lookup over a fixed decoder library; JumpReLU modifies only selector thresholds, not decoder exportability.","This round is a strict matched architecture probe: keep `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` explicitly pinned, and change only `ARCHITECTURE`.","Judge family worthiness using `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside final FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total online/runtime cost rather than FVU alone."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields. After `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` and `lowrank_gated_residual` both failed to pressure the mainline, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is the highest-value remaining feasible matched probe because it preserves LUTurbo exportability, stays in the low-EF budgeted regime, and tests a simpler thresholded selector that could reduce total online complexity if quality holds up. The main risk is that historical evidence for JumpReLU-style selectors has been weak, so this may mainly confirm that a single-stage thresholded low-rank branch cannot recover enough quality.","summary":"Run one valid matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` while keeping the `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, `LR=3.0e-3` mainline recipe fixed. This cleanly tests whether a thresholded single-stage low-rank selector is worth any continued attention under LUTurbo-compatible low-EF constraints.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0159.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.75x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并且比当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x 更低。当前 round 159 只允许一个 matched architecture probe，因此保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 以及主要 recipe 完全不变，仅将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成其最邻近的单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，第二阶段 residual refinement 是否仍然值得保留，还是单阶段 soft-codebook 版本已经提供了更优的系统级 cost-FVU 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显落后于 two-stage 主线，则说明第二阶段 refinement 在当前低 EF regime 下仍然有价值，下一轮回到主线继续 recipe 轴。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与 two-stage 接近且成本更低，则记录其为更强的低成本备选 family，但下一轮仍按要求回到当前主线。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 本身值得重新审视，但本轮只做架构价值判断，不立即连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更低 FVU 或更低成本误判为吞吐波动导致的假信号。","该 probe 的核心问题不是刷新 frontier，而是判断 two-stage 结构增量在当前可部署低 EF regime 下是否仍然值得继续。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 而不是更远的 topk 或 factorized_topk，是因为它是当前主线的最近父节点，能最干净地隔离“第二阶段 residual refinement 本身是否值得”这个问题，同时还能给出更低 selection_cost 的直接对照。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为其单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断第二阶段 refinement 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍然值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0216.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214 与 r215 已证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定改善 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，且最新一轮 K=192 反而把总耗时降到 302s，未出现明显吞吐惩罚；因此本轮继续沿同一最短链路 family 只把 K 提到 224，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.47x、继续留在 <0.5x 区域的前提下，把当前最佳低开销 FVU 从 0.1635 进一步压低，并判断 topk@EF1 的边际收益是否开始接近饱和。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K224 继续明显改善 FVU 且吞吐未恶化，则低开销前沿仍可沿 K 轴补一个更高点。","如果 K224 的收益已明显变小或训练代价开始恶化，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 的边际收益接近耗尽，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 仍是当前 <0.5x 区域最稳、最短链路、最易导出的直接兼容 family，已连续三次给出可解释的 Pareto 改善。","r215 在 total_cost=0.44x 处把 FVU 压到 0.1635，且运行代价未恶化，因此当前最高信息量单变量仍是 K 轴，而不是回到 repeatedly policy-reject 的 lowrank_factorized_residual param_only。","评估时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认新增查表预算是否仍值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮延续已验证有效的低开销 topk 主线，选择 K=224 而不是直接冲到 256，是为了继续留在 <0.5x 区域内补点，避免过早踩到 0.5x 边界。风险是 K 继续增大后 FVU 收益可能开始递减，但这正是当前需要量化的关键问题。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 224，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1635 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
