research/history/logs/agent_action_0004.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"topk/signum 在 1e-3 上已经优于 8e-4，说明当前主线仍处于“加大学习率能改善收敛”的区间；本轮只把 LR 小幅上调到 1.2e-3，检验收益是否还能继续延续，还是已经开始进入不稳定区。","summary":"继续围绕 topk 主线推进，不开新 family，不换优化器，不动 K。本轮唯一主变量是学习率：从 1e-3 小幅上调到 1.2e-3，回答“signum+topk 的更优 LR 是否在 1e-3 之上”这个单一问题。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮仍然严格遵守单变量原则，并延续当前最强主线配方做局部 LR 外推，归因清晰。风险是 1.2e-3 可能开始带来震荡或后段恶化，但这正是当前最该确认的信息；若出现不稳，就有充分依据结束 signum 的 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 维度。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.2e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 4 继续只调 LR，基于 r3 的改进结果向 1e-3 以上做小步外推。","当前重点不是只看最终 FVU，而是判断 1.2e-3 的曲线是否仍平滑下降，还是开始出现更大震荡和后段退化。","如果 1.2e-3 不再改善或稳定性变差，可认为 signum 的主线 LR 最优区间已接近 1e-3，下一轮应按顺序切换 optimizer。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 1.2e-3 继续改善且曲线稳定，下一轮可继续只调 LR 做更细化上探。","如果 1.2e-3 与 1e-3 接近但更不稳，下一轮应结束 signum 的 LR 扫描并只改 optimizer。","如果 1.2e-3 明显更差或震荡增大，说明 signum 的合适 LR 峰值已在 1e-3 附近，下一轮切换 optimizer 更有价值。"],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0201.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"}],"expected_win":"clarify_frontier","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"active_baseline_probe","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe under the fixed mainline recipe. Final reconstruction formula is x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i. This is LUTurbo 扩展兼容 because the low-rank trunk term U(Vx) can be exported as a static trunk vector library, the soft codebook term Σ_m pi_m c_m uses a static codebook library, and the sparse residual term Σ_i alpha_i b_i uses a static residual dictionary, so LUTurbo/Lottable inference remains static lookup plus weighted summation plus optional residual compensation. Holding K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, and LR=3.0e-3 fixed, this probe isolates whether the second residual refinement stage in lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual is actually buying enough FVU to justify its extra encoder selection cost and runtime overhead in the feasible low-EF regime.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual mainline next round as required by policy.","If lowrank_soft_codebook_residual is close in FVU while materially faster or cheaper at the same K/EF recipe, treat the second residual stage as weak value in the current LUTurbo-compatible regime."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility label: 扩展兼容.","This is a parent-family matched probe, not a new incompatible line: same trunk+codebook decomposition, only removes the second sparse refinement branch.","Selection-cost rationale: this family is comfortably feasible at EF=2 and materially cheaper than the two-stage parent, making it the cleanest architecture-only test of whether stage-2 refinement is worth keeping.","Judge the result using both FVU and runtime counters (tokens_per_sec, total wall time, final_total_tokens), because recent rounds show meaningful throughput drift."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the one-variable rule and avoids the previously policy-rejected asymmetric candidate. It is the most informative matched probe because it differs from the current mainline by exactly one structural element: the existence of the second residual stage. More distant probes like factorized_topk or lowrank_residual answer broader questions but are less diagnostic for the current mainline family.","summary":"Probe ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_soft_codebook_residual with the mainline K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3 recipe unchanged. This directly tests whether the extra second-stage residual refinement in the current mainline is worth its added online selection cost and runtime in the LUTurbo-compatible low-EF setting.","touched_files":[]}
