research/history/logs/agent_action_0021.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 20 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=4` is effectively past the practical floor: the late-phase FVU curve flattened completely while dead-feature pressure rose to about `0.68`, so further low-K descent is no longer the right question. This round changes only `K`, moving from the quality anchor side to `K=96`, to test whether LUTurbo can obtain a materially cheaper but still high-quality deployment point that may be more practical than the stressed ultra-low-K regime.","summary":"Shift the K sweep from the collapsed extreme low end to the unexplored moderate-cost region: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and set `K=96` to measure whether a near-anchor quality point exists between the current `K=64` and `K=128` frontier points.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active `topk` mainline, changes exactly one primary variable (`k`), respects the fixed `EF=12` rule and allowed-K set, and asks a single clean frontier question. The main risk is that `K=96` may add little beyond interpolation, but after `K=4` and `K=8` showed strong capacity stress, probing the moderate-K gap is a more deployment-relevant use of the same single-axis budget than continuing to push or retread the collapsed low end.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"96"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 20 (`K=4`) appears to mark the hard lower bound of the current topk/signum regime: late improvement vanished while `dead_pct` climbed to about `0.68` and `auxk` remained around `0.58`.","The current useful low-K region is likely above `K=8`, with `K=16` looking much more plausible than `K=8` or `K=4` for deployment-aligned tradeoffs.","Given the hard low-end boundary is now mapped, the next most informative single-variable K question is whether `K=96` provides a stronger quality-cost sweet spot between the existing `K=64` and `K=128` points."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=96` is very close to `K=128` in both final FVU and curve shape, it may become the practical high-quality reduced-cost default for this family.","If `K=96` lands roughly on interpolation between `K=64` and `K=128`, the K frontier on this recipe is likely sufficiently mapped and the next round should return to recipe tuning.","If `K=96` underperforms unexpectedly, re-check whether the current topk recipe is over-specialized to either very high or very low K and then move back to one recipe axis."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0008.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"在 signum 下把 LR 从 8e-4 提升到 1.8e-3 后，frontier 最优仍停在 1.6e-3，说明继续在 signum 上做更高 LR 外推的价值开始下降；本轮只切换优化器到 adam，并保持 topk/K128/EF12/LR=1.6e-3 不变，用来判断优化器本身是否能带来更稳的训练曲线和更好的 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕 topk 主线推进，不开新 family，不动 K。本轮按推荐顺序从学习率扫描切到优化器比较；唯一主变量是 OPTIMIZER：从 signum 改为 adam，同时保持 ARCHITECTURE=topk、K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=12、LR=1.6e-3 不变。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则，也符合“先调学习率，再换优化器”的主线顺序。风险是 adam 直接沿用 1.6e-3 未必是其最佳 LR，但作为 optimizer 首轮对照这是可接受的，因为它能最大限度隔离优化器效应；若结果有潜力，下一轮再只调 adam 的 LR。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 8 结束 signum 的主线 LR 上探，开始 topk family 内的 optimizer 对照。","r7 没有刷新 frontier，说明当前不能只追更高 LR，需要比较优化器对曲线形状和稳定性的影响。","本轮固定 LR=1.6e-3 做 adam 首轮对照；如果可行，下一轮应只调 adam 的 LR。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 adam@1.6e-3 比 signum@1.6e-3 更稳且更优，下一轮继续留在 topk family，只调 adam 的 LR。","如果 adam@1.6e-3 可运行但偏不稳或偏弱，下一轮仍只调 LR，给 adam 一轮学习率回调。","如果 adam 明显不如 signum 且没有曲线优势，可结束该优化器分支并回到 signum 主线。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0152.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"该 matched probe 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主线参考配方一致，仅把 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 topk，这一轮只回答一个问题：在当前低 EF 预算内，若去掉 low-rank trunk、soft-codebook coarse branch 与 two-stage refinement，只保留最朴素的单库稀疏选择，重构质量会退化到什么程度，从而判断当前主线复杂结构是否确实提供了值得继续投入的架构价值。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 topk 在大幅更低 selection_cost 下仍与主线接近，则说明当前主线复杂结构的总成本优势需要重新审视，下一轮按规则回到主线后应优先考虑更贴近总成本目标的简单 family。","若 topk 明显更差，则说明当前主线的 low-rank trunk + soft-codebook + staged refinement 组合在 EF=2 下仍有真实结构价值，下一轮回到主线继续做单变量 recipe 或成本轴工作。","若 topk 更快但质量远差，则把它保留为低成本 sanity baseline，不再继续占用主线轮次。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是单次 matched architecture probe，严格只改 architecture，其余 K、EF、optimizer、LR 全部与主线参考配方一致。","topk 为直接兼容 family，不属于不兼容候选，可合法作为兼容 frontier 的架构对照。","r150 与 r151 已经表明去掉 second stage 或去掉 soft-codebook 后 FVU 都明显变差；本轮进一步测试最简单单库 baseline，可帮助量化当前主线相对朴素 LUTurbo 兼容方案的真实结构增益。","评估时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分更高吞吐是否只是来自结构更简单而非更优的总成本-质量权衡。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守本轮架构探针规则：只改 architecture，保持主线的 K、OPTIMIZER、LR、EXPANSION_FACTOR 与主要 recipe 不变。相比重复已明显落后的近邻 family，这个 probe 提供了最强的低成本下界对照，能更清楚回答当前主线复杂结构是否值得继续。","summary":"执行一次严格 matched architecture probe：把当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成最简单的 topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断当前主线复杂结构相对直接兼容单库方案是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
