research/history/logs/agent_action_0226.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family: group_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；group_topk 只改变在线选择机制为“先组内竞争，再跨组保留最终 K 个激活”，不改变 decoder 端的静态向量库加权和形式，因此对 LUTurbo/Lottable 属于直接兼容，可直接导出到现有“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。相对当前低成本锚点 topk，本轮只改一个结构点：ARCHITECTURE 从 topk 改为 group_topk，保持 EF=1、K=248、LR=0.003、signum、AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 不变，测试 grouped selector 是否能在 <0.5x 区域改善 FVU。已核对 selection_cost_estimate：在 EF=1、K=248 下，group_topk 与 topk 的 selection=0.25x、deployment=0.24x、total=0.49x 完全一致，满足硬预算。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 group_topk 在 0.49x 同成本下优于 topk@K248 的 FVU=0.1462，且 tokens_per_sec 与总时长没有显著恶化，则保留该 family，并在下一轮只改 GROUP_TOPK_SIZE 做单变量细化。","如果 group_topk 与 topk 质量接近但运行代价更差，则将其仅记为历史参考，不继续占用 <0.5x 主战场轮次。","如果 group_topk 明显差于 topk，则关闭这条裸 grouped selector 支线，下一轮转向另一条同成本或近邻成本的新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["group_topk 的 LUTurbo 兼容性标签为直接兼容：最终重构仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和，grouping 仅作用于在线 selector。","已确认 cost 与 topk@EF1,K248 完全匹配：selection 0.25x，deployment 0.24x，combined 0.49x，因此结果可直接解释为同成本 selector 比较。","历史上 group_topk 在高 EF 裸试偏弱，但那是旧高成本 regime；本轮价值在于重新评估它在低 EF、短选择链路、严格预算下是否仍然过强约束。"],"self_review":"这是一轮严格的单变量架构探针，只改 ARCHITECTURE，不混入 K、EF、LR、AUX 或新 tunable。family 已存在且接线完成，不需要改 sparsify/ 或 AutoResearch 链路。主要风险是组约束在无 coarse branch 的单库裸结构上仍可能过强，但相比继续做 topk 微调，这轮对 <0.5x frontier 的信息增益更高。","summary":"运行一次同成本低开销架构探针：以当前最佳 low-cost topk 配方为基线，只将 ARCHITECTURE 切到 group_topk，测试 grouped selector 能否在保持 0.49x 总成本和直接兼容导出形式不变的前提下，把 <0.5x 区域的 FVU 继续向下压。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0210.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 u_r 是静态 trunk 向量库，b_i 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算系数 beta_r 与 alpha_i，并在 LUTurbo/Lottable 端导出为两个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此属于扩展兼容。r209 对 topk@EF1,K96 的继续加大查表预算被 policy 拦截，说明单纯沿 topk 的 K 轴上探不稳；本轮保持 K=64、EF=1、optimizer、LR 不变，只把 architecture 从 topk 切到 lowrank_factorized_residual，测试在仍瞄准 <0.5x 区域的前提下，加入极轻 low-rank trunk 与 factorized residual scorer 后，是否能显著优于 topk@0.31x 的 FVU。按现有成本表外推，该配置有希望落在低开销区或其边界附近，同时提供比纯单库 topk 更强的表达。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 lowrank_factorized_residual@EF1,K64 成功落入 <0.5x 且明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则下一步固定该 family，单变量扫描 K 或 TRUNK_RANK，补齐低开销前沿。","如果该配置仍超出 <0.5x 或 FVU 改善有限，则说明低开销区需要更短链路而非增加 trunk 分支，下一步应回到 topk/factorized_topk 或探索更小静态库方案。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库加 residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。","本轮只改 architecture，保持 K=64 和 EF=1 不变，便于判断在同等低字典规模与相近 lookup 预算下，增加轻 trunk 是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"该提案遵守单变量原则，并直接回应 r209 的 policy_reject：不再继续沿 topk 的 K 轴加预算，而是测试更有信息量的新低成本 family。主要风险是 deployment 侧 trunk 成本可能把 total_cost 推到 0.5x 附近甚至略上，但这仍能为低开销区提供关键边界信号。","summary":"切换到扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual，固定 K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，只改变 architecture，验证轻量 trunk+residual 结构能否在低开销区附近拿到明显优于 topk 的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0089.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `lowrank_residual_vq`, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`, `lowrank_gated_residual`, and `lowrank_grouped_residual` all failed to challenge the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative remaining matched architecture probe is the plain `lowrank_residual` family. It preserves the same low-rank trunk and static-library weighted-sum export path while removing the extra second residual stage and auxiliary selector structure, making it the cleanest test of whether the current mainline's quality advantage truly requires two-stage residual allocation. If `lowrank_residual` is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then the simpler single-stage low-rank family is not worth continuing in the current LUTurbo-aligned regime.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the matched architecture probe rule by changing only `architecture` and keeping the mainline `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe fixed. `lowrank_residual` is the strongest remaining LUTurbo-aligned probe because it is the simplest low-rank static-library decomposition still comparable to the current mainline, and it directly tests whether the second residual pass is buying necessary quality or only extra online cost. The main risk is that the family may underfit badly at matched K128, but that negative result would still answer the exact worth-continuing question cleanly.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 89 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness test for the simplest low-rank single-stage residual decomposition; the core question is whether dropping the second residual stage can preserve enough quality to justify the lower expected online cost.","Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not chain another new-family probe immediately after this one."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `lowrank_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-cost branch but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
