research/history/logs/agent_action_0213.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库，{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算系数 beta_r 与 alpha_i，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时可拆成 trunk 库查表加权和与 residual 库查表加权和，两部分都满足静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已在当前 family 上拿到 0.69x / 0.1256 且 tokens_per_sec 约 166.6k、总耗时 291s，当前最值得回答的单一问题不是再换 family，而是该点的高成本是否主要由 trunk 过宽导致；本轮仅将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 16，测试能否在保持明显优于 topk@0.31x 的 FVU 前提下，把 total_cost 尽量压向并最好压入 <0.5x 区域。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 进入 <0.5x 且 FVU 仍明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则固定该 family 后只沿 K 轴补一个点。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 的 FVU 明显崩塌或训练代价没有进一步优势，则说明 lowrank_factorized_residual 在低开销区仍过度依赖 trunk 容量，后续应回到更短链路 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["r210 说明 lowrank_factorized_residual 在低 EF 下具备很强质量潜力，且运行吞吐优于近期 topk 线；当前主要矛盾是成本而非训练不稳。","TRUNK_RANK 同时影响 encoder 与 deployment 两侧成本，是把该 family 从 0.69x 拉回低开销区的最高信息量单变量旋钮。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 trunk_rank，不再重复声明 K、EF、optimizer、LR，避免再次触发 param_only 的多主轴拒绝。选择 16 而不是 32，是因为目标是优先补 <0.5x 区域覆盖；更激进地下压 trunk 才更可能一次性把该高质量点推进到低开销前沿，但风险是 coarse trunk 表达会被过度削弱。","summary":"在扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual 上做一次低开销 param-only 探索：仅将 TRUNK_RANK 设为 16，验证能否以更小 trunk 库把当前 0.69x/0.1256 的高质量点推进到 <0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0065.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With the `gated` mainline stalled for twelve rounds and recent single-stage selector probes (`group_topk`, `bucketed_topk`, `codebook_topk`) all failing to beat it, the next highest-value matched architecture probe is `two_stage_residual`: it remains LUTurbo-compatible because the reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over static libraries, but distributes the fixed `K=128` budget across two sequential residual passes. This round answers one question only: under the matched `signum`/`LR=2.0e-3`/`EF=12` recipe, is that staged residual decomposition intrinsically strong enough to justify any later follow-up, or should it be ruled out immediately.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `two_stage_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the Round 65 policy by changing exactly one primary variable: architecture. `two_stage_residual` is a more informative remaining probe than batch-coupled top-k variants because it stays single-sample deployable, and it tests a distinct multi-stage static-library decomposition that is closer to LUTurbo's lookup-plus-selective-compensation execution model than another small selector tweak.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 65 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `two_stage_residual` after recent single-stage selector variants all underperformed matched `gated`.","`two_stage_residual` is extended-compatible with LUTurbo because its final reconstruction can be exported as the sum of two fixed-size sparse weighted sums over static decoder libraries, with a fixed stage split of the total `K`.","Judge this probe strictly as a family-worthiness test against matched `gated` K128: if it is clearly worse, discard it and return to the `gated` mainline next round; if it is competitive, record the result but still return to the mainline per policy."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_stage_residual` is clearly worse than matched `gated`, discard the family and return to the `gated` mainline next round.","If `two_stage_residual` is roughly competitive, record it as a possible staged lookup-plus-compensation direction but still return to the `gated` mainline next round per policy.","If `two_stage_residual` unexpectedly beats matched `gated`, schedule at most one later follow-up after the mandated return to the `gated` mainline."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0170.json:23:    "self_review": "This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields. After the recent asymmetric, gated, and jumprelu probes failed to pressure the mainline, the highest-value remaining matched probe is the strongest cheaper parent `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`: it preserves the same formula class except for removing the second residual stage, stays within the EF=2 budget, and directly tests whether that extra stage is actually earning its cost in the current deployable regime. The main risk is limited novelty because this family is already known historically, but it is still the cleanest remaining architecture-worthiness question under the forced probe policy.",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0029.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 28 showed that `whitened_topk` is not worth continuing: under a matched probe it failed catastrophically, so the next and only remaining useful question in this probe slot is whether a different directly compatible support-selection variant has any architectural merit at all. `gated` preserves the same static-dictionary weighted-sum reconstruction form as `topk` while changing only how support is selected and scaled, so this round asks a single yes/no question: is `gated` competitive enough under a matched K128/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF12 probe to justify any future follow-up.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe on `gated`. Keep `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and the current stabilized runtime/aux recipe fixed, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `topk` to `gated` to test whether this directly export-compatible family is worth continuing.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the matched-probe rule by changing only the architecture axis, keeps the core mainline recipe fixed, and selects a family that remains compatible with LUTurbo's static-vector weighted-sum deployment contract. The main risk is that the extra gating branch may add training complexity without improving quality or runtime-aligned sparsity behavior, but that is exactly the family-worthiness question this probe is intended to answer before returning to the topk mainline.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 28 ruled out `whitened_topk` as a promising matched probe candidate because it was massively worse than the topk control.","`gated` remains directly compatible with LUTurbo deployment because the final reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over a static decoder library with fixed `K`; the change is confined to encoder-side gating and support scoring.","Judge this round as a pure family-worthiness probe against the stabilized K128 topk control: if it is clearly worse or unstable, archive it and return to topk next round; if it is competitive, record that but still return to the mainline per policy."],"next_hypotheses":["If `gated` is clearly worse than matched `topk`, archive it immediately and return to the topk mainline next round.","If `gated` is competitive but not clearly better, record it as a plausible alternative family and still return to the topk mainline next round.","If `gated` beats the matched `topk` control, schedule at most one later follow-up after the mandated return to the mainline."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0135.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"architecture_value_signal","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"候选架构的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。low-rank trunk 基库 U 与 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 matched architecture probe 严格保持主线的 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变，只把 architecture 改为更简单的 lowrank_residual，用来回答一个问题：在当前低 EF 可行区间内，soft codebook coarse branch 是否仍然必要，还是 low-rank trunk + 单阶段 residual 已足够形成更优的成本/时延权衡。该架构在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 约 0.62x h×n，低于当前主线的 1.25x，若 FVU 没有明显恶化且运行更快，则值得作为低成本备选继续保留。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_residual 的 FVU 接近主线且吞吐更好，则说明当前 EF=2 下 coarse codebook 的边际收益有限，下一轮回到主线后应重新审视更简单 family 的成本优势。","若 lowrank_residual 明显劣于主线，则说明 soft codebook coarse branch 在低 EF 下仍然必要，下一轮回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续做成本轴微调。","若 lowrank_residual 介于主线与 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 之间且更快，可将其记为低成本备用点，但不替代当前最佳 FVU 主线。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮仍是单次 matched architecture probe，严格保持 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只改 architecture。","lowrank_residual 为扩展兼容 family，且在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 明显低于当前两阶段主线，适合回答 coarse codebook 是否必要。","r134 的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual probe 被 policy_reject，因此本轮改用另一个已知兼容且更低成本的父节点进行架构价值判断。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守本轮架构探针约束，没有联动改 recipe。选择 lowrank_residual 而非继续重复被拒的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual probe，可以更直接测试 soft codebook 分支本身的必要性；风险是该 family 可能在 K=128 下 FVU 明显偏弱，但这正是探针需要确认的信号。","summary":"做一个新的 matched architecture probe：仅把 architecture 改为 lowrank_residual，其余保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变，测量去掉 soft codebook 与第二阶段 refinement 后，这个更低成本父节点是否还值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0223.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LR","value":"3.6e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r222 已证明在 `topk@EF1,K248` 上去掉 auxiliary-K loss 与 r218 基本等价，说明当前 <0.5x 最强锚点的 loss 轴已没有明确收益；因此下一步应按开放假设转向同一锚点上的单变量 LR probe。基于低成本 signum 主线上历史上“2.4e-3 -> 3.0e-3` 往往优于向下回退，而当前 `topk@EF1,K248` 曲线仍显示 late-stage 仍在缓降，本轮严格锚定有效参考轮 r222，仅把 `LR` 从 `3.0e-3` 上调到 `3.6e-3`，测试更积极的步长能否在不改变 total_cost 的前提下，把 <0.5x 区域最佳 FVU 从 0.1462 再向下压，同时检查是否会像历史高 LR probe 一样带来吞吐下降或总时长恶化。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LR=3.6e-3` 在保持接近当前吞吐与总 token 的同时把 FVU 压到 0.1462 以下，则下一轮对该更高 LR 配方做一次 clean repeat，确认它是新的低成本 topk 锚点。","如果 `LR=3.6e-3` 与 `3.0e-3` 基本等价但运行代价更差，则关闭 topk 主线的向上 LR 分支，并把 topk recipe 空间暂时视为已基本饱和。","如果 `LR=3.6e-3` 明显退化或显著拖慢训练，则恢复 `LR=3.0e-3` 作为 topk 低成本锚点，下一轮转向新的低成本 family 而不是继续在 topk 上做 recipe 试探。"],"notes_to_memory":["r222 表明在 `topk@EF1,K248` 低成本主线上，`AUXK_ALPHA` 不是关键因子；后续应优先检查 LR 或转向新 family，而不是继续做 loss 轴清洗。","本轮不改变 decoder 端导出形态，也不改变 selection/deployment 成本；它只回答当前最强 <0.5x 锚点是否还存在纯优化层面的剩余空间。","评估本轮时必须同时比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、duration_sec 与 final_total_tokens；若只有极小 FVU 收益但训练明显更慢，应视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":222,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效 reference r222 只改 `LR`，family、K、EF、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA` 及所有结构参数保持不变。选择向上探到 `3.6e-3` 而不是先下探，是因为当前低成本 signum 主线的已知证据更支持“较大步长可能还有收益”，而不是立即回退到更保守设置；主要风险是更高 LR 可能带来与历史相似的运行时恶化，因此必须把系统代价与终点质量一起判读。","summary":"相对 r222 的 `topk@EF1,K248,AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 做一次严格 param_only LR probe，仅把 `LR` 上调到 `3.6e-3`，验证当前最强 <0.5x 低成本锚点是否还能通过更积极的 signum 步长进一步压低 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0198.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和。gated selector 只改变在线选择与系数调制路径，不改变 decoder 端的有限加权和形式，因此能够导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，lowrank_gated_residual 是否能在仍满足选择成本预算的情况下，相比 plain lowrank_residual 提供更好的 FVU；若它仍明显落后于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与主线，则说明 gate 作为 residual-side selector 改造在当前低 EF regime 下不值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_gated_residual 仍明显劣于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若它仅小幅优于 lowrank_residual 但训练更慢或选择成本更高，则将 gating 视为负面信号，不再继续占用 probe 轮次。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_gated_residual 的导出路径仍是 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态字典库的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","r193-r197 已基本排空 plain/factorized/direct-compatible 低成本路线；本轮补测 gated residual，判断 gating 是否只在强 soft-codebook backbone 上才可能有价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，问题明确且与前几轮不重复：验证 residual 家族中的 gating 是否值得保留。它不改变最终部署公式，只隔离 selector 机制本身的贡献，适合在当前 probe 阶段为 residual-side 改造补全证据。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 lowrank_gated_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构仍是 trunk 静态库与 residual 静态字典库上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即 residual-side gating 是否足以让该 family 继续作为 LUTurbo 兼容候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/round0026_standard_1774532341.config.json:2:  "architecture": "topk",
