research/history/round_summaries/round_0089.json:56:      "If `lowrank_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0089.json:57:      "If `lowrank_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-cost branch but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."
