research/history/round_summaries/round_0025.json:20:    "summary": "Run a clean full baseline on the exact active topk reference recipe. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, `K=128`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and explicitly lock the auxiliary/runtime knobs to their reference values so the next decision is grounded in a fresh comparable curve rather than in two regressed loss-side variants.",
