research/history/round_summaries/round_0058.json:81:      "Judge this probe by full curve shape and endpoint relative to the current `gated@128` anchor: if `topk` is clearly worse across the trajectory, archive it under the current matched recipe; if it is competitive, record that as evidence that the simpler architecture may still deserve a later dedicated revisit."
